[Student "S"]
{WEST bids 4\C, showing \H support, 13+ points and a singleton 
or void in \Cs.

EAST first shows her \DA, then, when WEST signs off, 
makes one more try by showing her \SA.

WEST finally gets inspired and bids the slam.}

