[Student "S"]
{NORTH has a very minimum 2NT bid, but when SOUTH shows \C shortness she can Control-bid 
her \HA without showing extra values.

SOUTH's hand became huge when he heard about NORTH's \HA. 
When Blackwood shows they hold three Aces he bids what he expects to be a comfortable slam.}

